Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.41,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In ancient times there was a heavenly blade...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.42,0:00:08.97,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,which gave its wielder great power: the legendary holy sword, Langrisser.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.37,0:00:12.72,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Greedy ambitions drove men to attempt to steal it...
