Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.83,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Much blood was spilt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.24,0:00:30.66,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,However, the Baldea royal family, descended from ancient heroes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.67,0:00:34.14,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,has protected Langrisser throughout the ages.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.15,0:00:37.22,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But now, the peace is crumbling.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.83,0:00:42.19,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,His majesty, Dalshis Emperor Digos, has gathered a massive army...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.20,0:00:47.74,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,to lay siege to Baldea Castle and obtain Langrisser.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.54,0:00:55.13,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He wants to obtain the sword to realize his great ambitions of world conquest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.98,0:01:18.49,MainB,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A long time has passed, and now the seal of the cursed sword has been broken.
